Class ProfileList

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.meditrackr.models.ProfileList

  • public class ProfileList
extends java.lang.Object
    ProfileList: A list of profiles. Allows adding and removing elements (by both index and record), checking if a profile object exists in the array and retrieving the size of the list.
